{
  "stem": "1511.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because if you go there, the guys could take away the girls and did anything whatever they want and beat up the boys.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And you never came out alive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] from mine place to the school was quite to go, far away.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it wasn't like we have here sidewalks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was you have to jump through water, the water was everywhere.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was you know, like European style.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when I was going to school, it was in the summer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And three hooligans came across, like you see in [NON-ENGLISH] with the-- And they start joking, asking me, what's your name and so on.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they made dirty jokes at me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I was very scared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I escaped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I went to school, and that was going-- was-- was quite a walk from one place.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was a lot of this Polish and Jewish were too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But wasn't so organized.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We, we just mixed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We didn't tell who we are or something like that, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We-- I belonged to Hashomer Hatzair. when I grow up later, but everything was in between the Jewish quarters.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in 1939, it was the last year of my school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went for a trip to see Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I guess we never was any place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father treated me, I think it was 20 zlotys to go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we went away for a few days, to see where Pilsudski used to live.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Can I show the picture then?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We'll show it at the end.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we came and we saw all the-- he lived in a belvedere, it's just like the White House.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was his spoon and his bed and everything where he was living.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
